# Backlog Consolidator

```yaml
section: backlog
title: Backlog Consolidator
status: active
owner: {{ owner }}
created_at: {{ created_at }}
updated_at: {{ updated_at }}
type: consolidator
scope: backlog
detail_directory: {{ memory_root }}/backlog/
tags: [backlog, scrum, memory, consolidator]
```

This file is the synthetic consolidator for backlog items.

[@ref: Backlog memory rule](CONSTITUTION.md#constitution.agent-memory-management.backlog)

